细节测试的会计科目，而只是进行简单的复核。O 网传 55 页 PPT 举报德勤违规审计: 红黄蓝、中国外运、博奇环保被点名"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b37a479546b7bccd42a08302bcee2019_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442997674"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IneDd0+npn91yEAMaCDYwNzIxODMyIL/l84AGMAs4xQVAL3IJNDQyOTk3Njc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1612695890.5865824", "card_id": "Q_442621457", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 122}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "请您评价这位初中生的文笔，好吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "题主是一名初中生，对自己的文笔究竟如何非常迷茫。我很少听过他人的评价，所以提了这么一个显得非常班门弄斧的问题…"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442621457"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IneDd0+npn91yEAMaCDYwNjM4MjAxIP+U6IAGMA44sgFAMHIJNDQyNjIxNDU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1612695890.5868824", "card_id": "Q_437848762", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 377}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么我那么努力学习，却不如那些成天睡大觉的人考得好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/437848762"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IneDd0+npn91yEAMaCDU5NTc4MzgzINjXy/8FMAg4wAVAMXIJNDM3ODQ4NzYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}